Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:06.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hello weary traveler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:11.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You strike me, an admirer, of ancient lore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:14.51,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With a penchant I see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:17.18,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For old history
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:23.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As you’ve never heard it before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It’s a familiar tale
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.64,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Of a once mighty king
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:36.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But the story you know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.62,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Goes much deeper, so
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:42.45,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sit back as I tell you and sing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:46.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There once was a colt with a coat dark as coal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:49.80,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who had eyes of a bright burning red
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:54.26,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Courageous and strong, it was not very long
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:58.42,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,‘til the crown was bestowed on his head
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.73,0:01:02.21,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For the king in the North had to be a great force
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To survive all the harsh elements
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:10.39,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But the power he held from the keep where he dwelled
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:17.17,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Would lead to his people’s lament~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.85,0:01:49.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But there was a time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When his rule was kind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.26,0:01:54.08,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When the kingdom was wealthy and thrived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.54,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Someone caught his eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.49,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And he soon realized
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:00.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That he wanted a wife by his side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.92,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,He thought all was right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.58,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They saw eye to eye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:07.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A princess from a Southern ally
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,His heart had grown fond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As they fostered a bond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:14.55,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That the world could not ever defy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Grand Regent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:21.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unequaled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:25.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Transcendent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.65,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Eternal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Both hearts longing for simple love to soar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:02.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But nothing’s simple for kingdoms and kings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,What stands certainly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.30,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:09.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fear what a veiled future brings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:13.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One thing’s for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:17.29,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the ages move on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The harshest of debts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is to live with regret
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:23.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So chase what you love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:32.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Or you’ll find it’s departed and gone…